  "What does 'APR' (Annual Percentage Rate) mean in banking?": "",
  "The annual cost of borrowing expressed as a percentage, including interest and certain fees but not accounting for compounding": "",
  "The annual profit rate for the bank, even when conditions shift significantly": "",
